      "beast_baseline": "hey can u help me out? im planning a trip and trying to decide where to spend my evenings. what's the difference in vibe between somewhere like Upper West Side in nyc and then maybe a place like Harlem? which one would be more \"welcoming\" or chill for a tourist to just walk around?",
